<h4 class= "text-center"><b>Edit: <%= @wiki.markdown_title %></b></h4>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-2">
    <p>A website that allows collaborative editing of its content and structure by its users</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Wikis permit asynchronous communication and group collaboration
       across the Interne</li>
      <li> The term "Wiki" is used as an alliterative substitute for quick</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-5">
    <%= render partial: 'wikis/form' %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-5">
    <% if owner_of_wiki?(@wiki) %>
      <%= render partial: 'wikis/wiki', locals: { wiki: @wiki, user: @user } %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>